OL,3,CDad who 'lived and breathed' for young
OL,4,Cson killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA father-of-one who "lived and
OL,7,Fbreathed" for his young son has been
OL,8,Fkilled in a hit-and-run crash.
OL,10,FJohn Shelton, 48, from Manchester, had
OL,11,Fbeen cycling on the Great North Road,
OL,12,Fnear Micklefied, Leeds, when he was
OL,13,Fhit by a VW Golf on Ridge Road on
OL,14,FMonday, 28 April. He died at the scene.
OL,16,FThe car drove off and was later found
OL,17,Fburned out in the Potternewton area.
OL,18,FTwo men have been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
