OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Shelton's widow,
OL,7,FLucy, said he had a "warm heart".
OL,9,FShe added: "He lived and breathed for
OL,10,Four five-year-old son, who was our IVF
OL,11,Fmiracle, and we were making plans over
OL,12,Fthe coming months to make memories
OL,13,Fwith our son.
OL,15,F"John has been tragically taken from
OL,16,Fus following the horrific
OL,17,Fcircumstances of his death and life
OL,18,Fwill never be the same again.
