OL,6,F"He will be remembered as one of a
OL,7,Fkind and we will cherish our memories
OL,8,Fand they will live on as we navigate
OL,9,Fsupporting our son with a life without
OL,10,Fhis dad."
OL,12,FThe collision took place at about 2pm
OL,13,Fnear the premises of Ridge Road Energy.
OL,15,FDet Insp Paul Conroy, of the Major
OL,16,FCollision and Enquiry Team, said there
OL,17,Fwere "multiple active enquiries
OL,18,Fongoing".
